messages.message:
heads up! If you received a patch professor comment saying that UAT patches would be applied on 4/11, then you were bamboozled. UAT patches were applied on 4/4, and the next scheduled time to apply all staged UAT patches is 5/8.

*NOTE*: If you want UAT patches attached to your PR to be applied immediately to UAT, add the `patch-professor/apply-uat`  label to your pr
